  "texts": [
    "Although OpenAI curated it to eliminate redundancy and improve quality, it is nominally 45-terabytes worth of compressed text data.",
    "ChatGPT, the next version of GPT-3, is a general-purpose conversation chatbot based on the GPT-3 language model developed by OpenAI.",
    "It is designed to generate humanlike text based on a given prompt or conversation and has the ability to engage in natural, open-ended conversations on a wide range of topics (refer to https:// openai.",
    "com/ blog/ chatg pt/).",
    "Unlike previous versions which were designed to seek input requests via prompts, ChatGPT was trained in a conversation or dialog-based way using reinforced learning from human feedback."
